  <message id="gcw.language_file">English</message>

  <message id="gcw.welcome.title">Welcome to GnuCashew</message>
  <message id="gcw.welcome.body">
    <p>
      Welcome to GnuCashew!
    </p>

    <p>
      This project is in development.
    </p>

    <p>
      This is a running development-copy of the GnuCashew
      program.  At this point, not much is working.  The main
      'Accounts' tree-view is working, and double-clicking
      on an account opens the 'Account Register'.  The Account
      Register is working in view-mode only.  You can scroll
      up and down, and the editing works, but it does not save
      back to the database file.
      The menu items are mostly disabled, execpt for any menu
      item that is working.  The 'Business:Customer:Overview' is
      working.  The 'Assets:Savings' account has a few transactions in
      it for scrolling around.
    </p>

    <p>
      The source-generated doxygen files can be found here;
      <br />
      <a href="https://gnucashew.lorimarksolutions.com/dox/html/index.html">
               https://gnucashew.lorimarksolutions.com/dox/html/index.html
      </a>
    </p>

    <p>
      The source-code repository can be found here;
      <br />
      <a href="https://github.com/lorimark/gnucashew">
               https://github.com/lorimark/gnucashew
      </a>
    </p>

    <p>
      This project uses Wt (<a href="https://www.webtoolkit.eu/">wthttps://www.webtoolkit.eu/wt</a>) as the web rendering library.
    </p>

    <p>
      Feel free to poke around.<br />
      Have fun! Let me know what you think!<br />
      mark@lorimarksolutions.com
    </p>
    (press &lt;esc&gt; to continue)
  </message>

